Background

		Mr. Thomas A. Fillippo, Sr., also known as Tom, serves as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Devault Packing Company, Inc. Mr. Fillippo has been the President of Devault Foods, Inc. since 1972. Mr. Fillippo has been a Director of DNB Financial Corp. and its subsidiary DNB First National Association since February 22, 2006. He holds degree in Health and Physical Education from West Chester University.	
	



