Accidents & Personal Injury– Auto Accidents, Wrongful Death, Boating Accidents, Premises Liability/ Slip and Fall, Catastrophic Injuries, Products Liability, Motorcycle Accidents, Negligence Claims, Ovarian Cancer Talcum Powder Claims, Truck Accidents.

Civil Litigation– Auto Fraud, Consumer Protection, Injunctions, Insurance claims, Orders of protection, Qui tam – False Claims Act, University law, §1983 – Civil Rights Claims.

Employment Law– Wrongful Termination, Retaliation, Sexual Harassment,  Americans with Disabilities Act, Title VII, Gender Discrimination, Race Discrimination, Age Discrimination, Gender Discrimination, Religious Discrimination, Whistleblower Claims, EEOC Claims, Missouri Human Rights Act Claims, Hostile Work Environment.
DUI/DWI–  Boating Under the Influence (BUI), Commercial Drivers License Offenders (CDL), Driving Under the Influence (DUI)/ Driving while intoxicated (DWI).
Criminal Defense– Assault, Drug crimes, Felonies, Misdemeanors, Property crimes, Traffic crimes, White collar crimes, Gun Rights, Minor in Possession (MIP).

Business Law– Business Consultation, Business Formation, Contracts, Corporate Structure, Incorporation.










